                which deal either with certain diseases or diseases of certain parts of the eye.[HN] provides state-of-the-art care
                for all facets and stages of eye conditions. We use the latest techniques and therapies to administer routine eye examinations 
                offer various eye related treatments including glaucoma treatment in India.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
    


